::: MEGATRON throws his tiny arms above his body :::; Argh! Thats it! 
Shredder pick up Quickstrike now, we will go on by ourselfs.

::: He turns and begins to buzz away :::

~~~~~~~~

::: TRANSANULAS can hear HELL BEAST, GREMLIN, and JACKLE outside the sealed 
door. They were tring to gigure out how to get it open because the spider had 
used some webbing to seal it shut. For now he was safe. ::::

::: TRASANULAS went over to the comm systems. After a few configurations he 
thought he could send out a message...unfortunetly in was written in ancient 
Decepticon dialect so if the Oblitercons recived it they would have a hard 
time translating. :::

::: TRANSANULAS ::: Oblitercons! Please hurry with QUickstrike...I fear 
Megatron may be on his way to intercept you. He wants to kill me and take 
over the ship. And, HELL BEAST is holding my hostage. Its only a matter of 
time before he gets inside. Unless you get here soon...Ill have to activate 
your proto-form to use as a defense.

::: He ended the transmission and then thought about what form he would 
choose for the blank in the stasis pod. :::
